title: Full Metal Dojo
overview: Full Metal Dojo (FMD) is Thailand's largest Mixed Martial Arts promotion created with the goal to help promote MMA throughout Thailand and South East Asia. Founded by MMA's most interesting personality, Jon Nutt, the Full Metal Dojo team aims to follow in the footsteps of other pro organizations by providing a professional platform on which upcoming MMA fighters based in Thailand can put their skills to the tests.
